26
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,840
We had dumplings.

27
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,920
Mom, please. I'm hungry.

28
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:34,720
Help yourself.

29
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,360
Okay.

30
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,840
Make yourself at home.

31
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,560
Thank you.

32
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,360
Change your shoes.

33
