different from

36
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:51,840
what I made.

37
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:52,920
Dong,

38
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,240
you guys eat.

39
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,920
After that, go take a shower.

40
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,520
Tomorrow is the first day

41
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,400
