48
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,880
Come on,

49
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:11,720
isn't Jinghui

50
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,840
your good friend?

51
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:13,960
Be kind.

52
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,240
Thanks, Madam.

53
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:20,320
Mom,

54
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,080
wait a sec, let me finish eating.

55
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,760
I'll make the bed.

56
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,400
No, I'll do it.

57
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,760
I'll sleep on the couch tonight.

58
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,080
No way!

59
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,160
How could you,

60
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,160
as a guest, do this?

61
