64
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,200
It's quite big.

65
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,320
Can we?

66
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,440
Sure, it's settled.

67
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,200
Forget the couch.

68
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,080
Eat more, Jinghui.

69
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,400
Okay.

70
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,720
