74
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,640
No.

75
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,120
Never!

76
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,320
It's so cold.

77
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,320
Jinghui,

78
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:03,240
come on,

79
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,320
eat now

80
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,320
