81
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:07,440
Thank you.

82
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,120
This is for you.

83
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,080
What a feast!

84
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,040
This fish,

85
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,360
Dong made it.

86
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,680
His cooking is better than mine.

87
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,280
Try it.

88
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,760
You made this?

89
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:21,840
How's it?

90
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,800
It's pretty good.

91
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,040
Of course.

92
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,720
At least you won't starve

93
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,520
as a cook.

94
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,600
Absolutely.

95
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:32,640
Madam,

96
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:35,080
since you and Ling Dong cook,

97
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,040
I can't just eat for free.

98
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,440
I'll wash the dishes later.

99
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,400
No, you're our guest.

100
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,360
Eat more fish,

101
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,480
it's good for the brain.

102
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:42,840
You

103
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,400
