104
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,320
Eat more.

105
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:47,920
You too.

106
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:51,000
Right, not only is your brain slow,

107
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,800
but your feet stink.

108
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:53,480
Rumors,

109
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,400
complete nonsense!

110
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,200
You can say my brain is slow,

111
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,720
but stinky feet are just your nose

112
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,720
being too sensitive.

113
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,920
I'm just being honest.

114
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,240
Ignore him, ma'am, have more food.

115
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:07,840
Jinghui,

116
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,440
is there a tear

117
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,240
under the sleeve

118
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,240
of your elbow?

119
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:11,600
Where?

120
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,640
Pull it back, see?

121
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,280
Look, isn't it?

122
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,320
Oh, yes.

123
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,280
It's okay,

124
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,760
might've ripped it

125
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,960
playing basketball.

126
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:20,920
I didn't notice.

127
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,240
I'll just throw this away

128
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:22,840
and get a new one.

129
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,520
Don't.

130
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,440
I can

131
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,760
sew it up later.

132
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:26,880
Let's eat.

133
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,000
Have more.

134
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,360
Enjoy it.

135
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:32,880
Dong, you eat more too.

136
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:33,200
Okay.

137
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:34,360
Jinghui, if you like it,

138
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,720
come over more often.

139
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:38,080
That's cool.

140
00:08:38,800 --> 00:08:39,520
Hold on,

141
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,680
don't move.

142
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,760
Can you hear the ocean?

143
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:49,080
Yes, I hear the echo of wisdom.

144
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,600
Shouldn't it all be water?

145
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,480
How could it be?

146
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:54,400
I know what you mean by water.

147
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,360
The sea of knowledge.

148
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,960
Can't tell at all.

149
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,240
Mom, here you are.

150
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:08,160
Jinghui,

151
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,200
I don't think your shirt

152
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,000
can keep you warm.

153
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,480
It may just look good.

154
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,960
No, ma'am...

155
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:16,880
it can.

156
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,520
I didn't feel cold.

157
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,240
That's right,

158
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,800
you young boys

159
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,640
are full of energy.

160
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,560
Dong sometimes doesn't wear the clothes

161
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,040
I bought him 'cause he feels hot.

162
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:29,120
When did this happen?

163
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,840
Remember

164
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,160
the thermal underwear

165
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,720
I bought you?

166
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:34,960
You never wore it.

167
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,240
I was worried you'd be cold,

168
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,240
even got you

169
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,360
the thick kind.

170
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:49,520
Are you asleep?

171
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,000
I can't sleep.

172
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,880
Counting sheep then.

173
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,440
My grandma's coming back tomorrow.

174
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,240
Thank God.

175
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,240
You're finally leaving.

176
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,000
I'm gonna

177
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,960
have a nervous breakdown.

178
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,720
Would you stop saying that?

179
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,680
Exaggerating.

180
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,160
Didn't you complain about the hot water

181
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,240
and hard bed?

182
00:10:39,280 --> 00:10:40,080
Hurry up and leave.

183
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,040
But, to be honest,

184
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:46,600
I really like

185
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,640
staying at your place.

186
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:53,240
It feels just like home.

187
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,280
Goodnight.

188
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,600
Sweetheart,

189
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:37,840
did you miss me?

190
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,800
Of course,

191
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,160
I missed you so much.

192
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,240
Your dad had to

193
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:47,000
go abroad for work,

194
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,320
left early this morning.

195
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,040
Who cares about him?

196
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,080
Let's go inside.

197
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:52,720
Come on, Grandma.

198
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:53,880
I'll carry that.

199
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:54,720
It's okay.

200
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:55,680
Let's go.

201
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:57,600
