202
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:58,400
No,

203
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,840
I've been well taken care of by my friend.

204
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,480
You definitely haven't eaten properly.

205
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,160
No! I have!

206
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,240
My friend cooked for me.

207
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:05,680
Look at you...

208
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:18,520
Jinghui!

209
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,040
Jinghui.

210
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:22,720
Hi, Ma Yiming.

211
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,080
Did you miss me?

212
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,600
Disgusting.

213
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,120
Jinghui,

214
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,480
