215
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,120
What's wrong?

216
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,560
You don't love me anymore.

217
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:32,800
Get away.

218
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:36,560
Jinghui.

219
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:41,560
Ling Dong,

220
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,040
here's the breakfast I brought you.

221
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:44,240
Have a try.

222
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:45,920
Thanks.

223
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,400
How is it? Good?

224
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:55,600
Yeah.

225
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,960
What would you like

226
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,680
for tomorrow?

227
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,160
Thanks, but I can buy it myself.

228
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,800
No worries, there are

229
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:02,560
