230
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,400
I see,

231
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:06,680
well, thanks then.

232
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:10,360
By the way,

233
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,160
have you finished your homework?

234
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,080
Yes.

235
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,560
There are 2 questions

236
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,960
