237
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:17,760
I can

238
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:18,800
help you have a check.

239
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:19,480
Okay.

240
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,200
Sometimes,

241
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:24,560
