251
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,240
Let's go play basketball.

252
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:06,160
Go ahead.

253
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,360
Keke,

254
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,400
