255
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,360
No, is it good?

256
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:11,920
It's fantastic.

257
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:12,760
I'm telling you,

258
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:13,920
it's definitely the best one

259
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,880
I've seen this year.

260
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,320
Who did you go with?

261
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,040
My mom.

262
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,320
It was so awkward.

263
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:21,640
Oh my gosh,

264
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:23,000
shouldn't it

265
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,400
be watched with someone you like?

266
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:25,400
Exactly.

267
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,520
I'm so jealous of those

268
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:29,280
