269
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:32,720
Lan Jinghui, what are you doing?

270
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:34,960
Today's sunlight is so nice,

271
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:35,920
isn't it?

272
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:40,520
I'm serious,

273
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,960
that movie is amazing.

274
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:51,760
A Must-Watch for Couples!

275
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,640
This one?

