00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,560
Saturday night at 7:30 p.m.,

277
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:04,040
two tickets side by side.

278
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:07,520
Done.

279
00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:26,120
Good morning, Xiaohua.

280
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:28,480
Your breakfast.

281
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:32,240
Since you bring me

282
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:32,920
good food every morning,

283
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,520
as your master,

284
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,360
I want to tell you

285
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:37,000
some good news.

286
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:39,480
I don't care

287
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,960
