290
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,960
Not about basketball!

291
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:45,800
It's about Ling Dong.

292
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,560
What's wrong with him?

293
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:48,480
He...

294
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:54,720
wants to invite you to a movie.

295
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,200
But he's too shy to say so.

296
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,600
So he asked me to do it.

297
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,200
I had to

298
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:01,000
help him out.

299
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,360
Good news, right?

300
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,320
Anyway, the ticket code

301
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,200
